###########################################
## -- how to dizkneelande a desktop ---- ##
###########################################

- minimal install of arch
- sudo pacman -S --needed base-devel
- git clone https://github.com/dizkneelande/hyprland
- cd hyprland
- chmod +x install.sh
- ./install.sh
- wait for ages zzz
- reboot
- catppuccin the following: xfce-terminal, geany, papirus, grub, plymouth
- oh-my-bash: half-life theme
